@startuml
title MicroMeet - Activity Diagram (Manage Profile & Preferences)

start
:1. Open Profile screen;
:2. View current profile and preferences;
:3. Edit profile fields and preferences;
:4. Click "Save";
:5. System validates profile inputs;

if (Inputs valid?) then (Yes)
  :6. System loads user record;
  :7. System applies profile changes;
  :8. System updates preferences;
  :9. System saves updated user;
  :10. Show "Profile updated" confirmation;
else (No)
  :11. Show validation errors;
  :12. User revises inputs;
endif

stop

legend bottom
Steps mapping (numbers match actions):
1 Open Profile screen
2 View current profile/preferences
3 Edit fields/preferences
4 Click Save
5 Validate inputs
6 Load user record
7 Apply profile changes
8 Update preferences
9 Save updated user
10 Show confirmation
11 Show validation errors
12 Revise inputs
endlegend

@enduml